headline.main: PALESTINE RESTRICTS AMERICAN IMPORTS; Government to Control All the Licenses for Goods From U.S.

lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM, Oct. 31 -- Effective immediately the Palestine Government announces today the discontinuance of individual import licenses for a number of commodities imported from the United States but that limited supplies will be made available by the government provided they are necessary to insure the maximum war effort or to maintain the civilian community on a wartime basis.
